            "title": "Cactus Hunt",
            "summary": "There are three sizes of cactuses. Depending on which one you click&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>There are three sizes of cactuses. Depending on which one you click you get 1, 2 or 3 points. Pressing reset restarts the count at zero.</p>\n<p>The phone screams when you touch a cactus. Phones can’t deliver an electric shock yet, else that would have been an option. ;-)</p>\n<p>You are allowed to use the sounds and images.</p>\n<p>All images are from <a href=\"http://www.pixabay.com/\">www.pixabay.com</a> and are in the public domain.</p>\n<p>Sound are from here <a href=\"https://freesound.org/people/jorickhoofd/sounds/180345/\">https://freesound.org/people/jorickhoofd/sounds/180345/</a> with atribution https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/</p>\n<div class=\"gallery\"   >\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999316.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999316-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">The layout i made</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999317.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999317-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">All the components i used</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999318.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999318-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">All the assets i used</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999319.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999319-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">Defining lists</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999309.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999309-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">What should happen when the app opens</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999315.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999315-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">Add to score depending on the size of the cactus. Play a sound</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999314.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999314-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">What if you only hit the canvas</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999313.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999313-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">Update score</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999312.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999312-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">Ask to reset the score</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999311.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999311-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">What if yes is choosen</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999310.png\" ><img src=\"http://blog.petermathijssen.nl/media/posts/1/gallery/Selection_999310-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\"></a>\n<figcaption class=\"gallery-description\">Put a cactus random on the canvas</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/PeterMathijssen/aia/blob/master/cactushunt.aia\">Download</a> AIA file</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
